<p begin="618950000t" end="668550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;總有一天我會讓你看到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="669660000t" end="731660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;光輝閃耀的世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1217540000t" end="1247800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;什麼?兩個骷髏頭?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1262920000t" end="1286920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;我贏了,千萬不要恨我喔&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1295620000t" end="1325540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;喂,路克,你也過來玩吧?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1326650000t" end="1347240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;偶爾也跟我們一起玩嘛&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1376700000t" end="1396950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;不,我不玩了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1465790000t" end="1503450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;我又沒有怎麼樣&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;他居然突然發起飆來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1504500000t" end="1510070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;然後呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1511170000t" end="1535850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;夜神同學,你怎麼了嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1536860000t" end="1561770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;請你把這段文章翻譯一下&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1610270000t" end="1633590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;一定要遵從神的指示&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1634630000t" end="1673990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;這麼一來&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;海洋資源將變得更加豐富&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1675000000t" end="1693310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;也不會有暴風雨了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1707370000t" end="1727280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;今天上午11點左右&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1728390000t" end="1748640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;神奈川縣橫濱市的某公寓裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1749740000t" end="1794680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;發現一具年約30歲&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;全身沾滿血跡的男性屍體&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1795790000t" end="1824800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;神奈川縣警方判定這是殺人案件&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;開始進行調查&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1825820000t" end="1843790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;下一則新聞&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1844840000t" end="1859740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;今天中午過後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1860850000t" end="1897820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;一名居住在&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;東京都涉谷區的25歲女子&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1898890000t" end="1921530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;遭到性侵害後被殺身亡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1922580000t" end="1951930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;嫌犯是35歲的男子&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;兔富士直樹&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1952950000t" end="1973200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;已經以殺人罪嫌逮捕&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1986650000t" end="2000980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;每天每天&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2019010000t" end="2038010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;重複著同樣的事情&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2057720000t" end="2085020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;真是的,無聊透了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2101090000t" end="2116670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;這個世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2117780000t" end="2130060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;真是爛透了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2137130000t" end="2166480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;第1話 新生&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2218210000t" end="2237210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;真的假的?你去那個海邊了?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2238230000t" end="2253810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;真是浪費時間&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2254910000t" end="2271860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;真想叫他退錢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2638960000t" end="2650560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;DEATH NOTE&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2659990000t" end="2683310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;直譯的話是死亡筆記本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2684340000t" end="2692300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;哼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2714370000t" end="2732680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;使用方法&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2733730000t" end="2777070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;名字被寫在&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這本筆記本裡的人就會死掉&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2805800000t" end="2815470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;無聊透了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2828820000t" end="2851460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;真是的,這個社會真的病了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2858520000t" end="2892190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;這跟不幸連鎖信一樣&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;完全沒有進步&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2901230000t" end="2926830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;名字被寫進去的人就會死掉?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3029350000t" end="3062680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;真是的,我八成也頭殼壞掉了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3096760000t" end="3134760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;腦中必須記得對方的長相,否則無效&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3135790000t" end="3144430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;因此&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3145470000t" end="3180050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;其他同名同姓的人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不會因此死亡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3187180000t" end="3196500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;寫完名字之後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3197520000t" end="3233810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;在人間界時間單位&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;40秒之內寫上死因的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3234890000t" end="3250470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;這個人就會因此死亡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3251580000t" end="3261820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;沒有寫的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3262920000t" end="3283510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;死因將全為心臟痲痺&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3291280000t" end="3317900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;寫完死因之後&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;還有6分44秒的時間&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3318980000t" end="3350950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;可以記述更為詳細的死亡過程&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3373700000t" end="3413060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;意思是可以決定讓他輕鬆的死&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;或是痛苦的死嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3414070000t" end="3449340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;惡作劇還設計得這麼詳細周到&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;還蠻行的嘛&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3521510000t" end="3547450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;寫上名字,那個人就會死掉…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3562220000t" end="3575530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;真的無聊透了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3738060000t" end="3748640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;等一下&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3749740000t" end="3780340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;萬一對方真的死了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我不就成了殺人犯?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3805460000t" end="3817400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;不可能&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3818480000t" end="3833380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;不可能有這種事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3846170000t" end="3884850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;昨天在新宿鬧區&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;傷害6名無辜路人的歹徒&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3885880000t" end="3938210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;挾持了幼兒和保姆8名人質&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;目前躲在這個托兒所裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3939260000t" end="3983860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;警視廳證實犯人是&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;42歲的待業中男子,音原田九郎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3984980000t" end="4003290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;警方將開始進行談判&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4072060000t" end="4101980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;40秒,死於心臟痲痺&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4127790000t" end="4144740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;目前還不太清楚詳細情況&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4154150000t" end="4179400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;最令人掛心的是人質的安全&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4180500000t" end="4190170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;是啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4196190000t" end="4219170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;以上是來自現場的最新報導&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4220210000t" end="4232490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;謝謝記者的報導&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4240230000t" end="4256500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;橋本先生,你有什麼看法?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4257580000t" end="4294210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;希望這個事件可以早點落幕&#x202c;</p>
