<p begin="7285610000t" end="7304950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle172">&#x202a;月,你真的很用功呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7305960000t" end="7317220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle173">&#x202a;是啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7318310000t" end="7344590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle174">&#x202a;那我去用功囉,不要吵我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7345670000t" end="7359320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle175">&#x202a;是,是&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7360350000t" end="7392320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle176">&#x202a;月,有沒有想要什麼東西?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7393380000t" end="7407710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle177">&#x202a;要什麼儘管說&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7408730000t" end="7428980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle178">&#x202a;媽媽,我沒有想要的啦&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7461120000t" end="7479430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle179">&#x202a;我想要的東西已經到手了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7673660000t" end="7689240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle180">&#x202a;看來你很喜歡它嘛&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7767760000t" end="7784370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle181">&#x202a;幹嘛嚇成這個樣子?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7793110000t" end="7828720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle182">&#x202a;我是這本筆記本的主人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;死神路克&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7835820000t" end="7855500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle183">&#x202a;看你剛才那個樣子&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7856510000t" end="7887110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle184">&#x202a;你應該已經知道&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這不是一本普通的筆記本吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7955610000t" end="7966870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle185">&#x202a;你是死神?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8011330000t" end="8031010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle186">&#x202a;我並沒有嚇到喔,路克&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8044700000t" end="8080990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle187">&#x202a;不,我一直在等你,路克&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8108760000t" end="8160070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle188">&#x202a;我原本就沒懷疑過&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;死神的筆記本是真是假&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8161150000t" end="8185150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle189">&#x202a;只是親眼目睹了各種事情之後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8186170000t" end="8211080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle190">&#x202a;我就能更加確信&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;進而採取行動&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8219870000t" end="8237160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle191">&#x202a;原來如此&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8238230000t" end="8261550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle192">&#x202a;反倒是我被你嚇到了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8262580000t" end="8327880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle193">&#x202a;我也曾經聽過&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;死亡筆記本曾出現在人間界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8328980000t" end="8367320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle194">&#x202a;但短短5天就做到這種地步&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你還是第一個呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8368360000t" end="8390310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle195">&#x202a;一般人會嚇得要命&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;無法寫這麼多&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8397720000t" end="8420700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle196">&#x202a;路克,我已經有心理準備了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8421740000t" end="8454050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle197">&#x202a;我是明知它是死神的筆記本&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;才開始用的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8455110000t" end="8470350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle198">&#x202a;接著死神來了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8477800000t" end="8492700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle199">&#x202a;我會有什麼下場?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8493810000t" end="8515760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle200">&#x202a;你會奪走我的靈魂嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8516840000t" end="8537770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle201">&#x202a;嗯?什麼東西啊?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8538860000t" end="8562180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle202">&#x202a;這是人類自己的幻想嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8573230000t" end="8596890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle203">&#x202a;我不會對你做任何事情&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8609600000t" end="8633600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle204">&#x202a;從它掉落在人間界的那一刻起&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8634620000t" end="8658280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle205">&#x202a;筆記本就是人間界的東西了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8659310000t" end="8689910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle206">&#x202a;換句話說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這本筆記本已經是你的了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8696680000t" end="8713290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle207">&#x202a;這是,我的…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8720710000t" end="8742320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle208">&#x202a;你不要的話,可以轉給別人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8749070000t" end="8788090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle209">&#x202a;不過,到時候我會刪掉&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你對於死亡筆記本的記憶&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8797120000t" end="8839780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle210">&#x202a;那麼,使用死亡筆記本&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;真的不需要付出任何代價嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8847830000t" end="8865460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle211">&#x202a;硬要說的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8866520000t" end="8907480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle212">&#x202a;筆記本的使用者會感受到&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;一般人所沒有的煩惱和恐懼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8922910000t" end="8946230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle213">&#x202a;還有你死掉時&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8947270000t" end="8989590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle214">&#x202a;我必須把你的名字&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;寫在我的筆記本上&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9000990000t" end="9024990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle215">&#x202a;使用過死亡筆記本的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9026010000t" end="9055020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle216">&#x202a;千萬別認為自己&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;可以上天堂或下地獄&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9071390000t" end="9082650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle217">&#x202a;就只有這樣而已&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9133450000t" end="9154040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle218">&#x202a;期待死後的樂趣吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9197180000t" end="9209120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle219">&#x202a;月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9210200000t" end="9231130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle220">&#x202a;沒關係,去開門吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9260910000t" end="9268530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle221">&#x202a;什麼事?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9269590000t" end="9286200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle222">&#x202a;媽拿蘋果來給你吃了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9287270000t" end="9307520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle223">&#x202a;鄰居分給我們的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9308630000t" end="9331950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle224">&#x202a;你的房間怎麼這麼暗&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9332990000t" end="9345270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle225">&#x202a;這樣眼睛會壞掉耶&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9346330000t" end="9361000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle226">&#x202a;這是怎麼回事?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9362010000t" end="9379640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle227">&#x202a;難道媽媽看不見嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9398050000t" end="9437640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle228">&#x202a;那本筆記本,原本是我的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9438760000t" end="9490750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle229">&#x202a;而你是目前的使用者&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;所以你當然看得見我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9491810000t" end="9521160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle230">&#x202a;當然我的聲音,也只有你聽得見&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9522170000t" end="9537750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle231">&#x202a;換句話說,死亡筆記本是&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9538860000t" end="9568780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle232">&#x202a;人類夜神月&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;和死神路克之間的聯繫&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9612930000t" end="9623850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle233">&#x202a;真好吃&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9624940000t" end="9663280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle234">&#x202a;那我再問你一個問題&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;為什麼選中我?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9678330000t" end="9693000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle235">&#x202a;你有沒有在聽?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9727380000t" end="9757070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle236">&#x202a;人間界的蘋果真好吃啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9758080000t" end="9771050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle237">&#x202a;這應該怎麼形容呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9780430000t" end="9788050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle238">&#x202a;鮮美多汁?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9789110000t" end="9803440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle239">&#x202a;回答我的問題!&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9814130000t" end="9830400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle240">&#x202a;我沒有選中你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9831480000t" end="9858100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle241">&#x202a;我只是搞丟我的筆記本而已&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9859180000t" end="9889100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle242">&#x202a;你以為你聰明過人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;才會被選上嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9890210000t" end="9900790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle243">&#x202a;別臭美了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9912560000t" end="9930190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle244">&#x202a;筆記本湊巧掉在這附近&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9931250000t" end="9946830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle245">&#x202a;然後湊巧被你撿到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9947930000t" end="9962260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle246">&#x202a;只是這樣而已&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9969960000t" end="10015580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle247">&#x202a;所以我才用人類最通用的英文&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;在上面附加說明&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10016670000t" end="10036350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle248">&#x202a;那你為什麼會搞丟?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10037360000t" end="10058970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle249">&#x202a;還好心的寫上使用方式&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10060050000t" end="10079390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle250">&#x202a;你可別說你是不小心搞丟的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10087070000t" end="10099690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle251">&#x202a;為什麼啊?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10108760000t" end="10125030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle252">&#x202a;因為太無聊了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10140790000t" end="10149770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle253">&#x202a;無聊?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10170490000t" end="10200410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle254">&#x202a;老實說,現在的死神都閒得要命&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10201520000t" end="10224500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle255">&#x202a;成天不是睡午覺就是賭博&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10239220000t" end="10267200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle256">&#x202a;要是在死亡筆記本&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;寫上名字的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10268250000t" end="10293500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle257">&#x202a;還會被笑說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;「幹嘛這麼賣力工作啊」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10302950000t" end="10336280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle258">&#x202a;把死神界的傢伙寫進筆記本&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;他們也死不了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10337320000t" end="10360640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle259">&#x202a;而我一直待在死神界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10361680000t" end="10396040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle260">&#x202a;就算殺死人間界的人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這樣一點也不好玩&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10412400000t" end="10440380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle261">&#x202a;所以我才來這裡&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;因為人間界來比較好玩&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10469120000t" end="10500400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle262">&#x202a;不過話說回來&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你真的寫了好多名字啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10501490000t" end="10543130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle263">&#x202a;為什麼只有&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;被大卡車撞死的傢伙有寫死因?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10551870000t" end="10586790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle264">&#x202a;因為不寫死因的話&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;大家都會死於心臟痲痺&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10587910000t" end="10612250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle265">&#x202a;這正是死亡筆記本最棒的地方啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10613260000t" end="10621900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle266">&#x202a;路克&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10638290000t" end="10672650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle267">&#x202a;等我把主要的罪犯名字寫完之後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10673660000t" end="10695960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle268">&#x202a;壞人的等級就會慢慢的降低&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10697010000t" end="10717260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle269">&#x202a;你這麼做有什麼目的?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10718370000t" end="10729630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle270">&#x202a;再怎麼笨的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10730720000t" end="10761660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle271">&#x202a;也會察覺到&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;有人正在消滅世上的壞人吧?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10769750000t" end="10805020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle272">&#x202a;我要讓全世界的人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;知道我的存在&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10806120000t" end="10832740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle273">&#x202a;知道有個正義使者在制裁壞人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10858180000t" end="10902210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle274">&#x202a;可是&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;下達正義的制裁又能如何?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10903220000t" end="10917210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle275">&#x202a;為什麼要做這種事?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10926910000t" end="10954890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle276">&#x202a;因為,我也很無聊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="10986970000t" end="11009270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle277">&#x202a;當然一開始我並不相信&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11010330000t" end="11027280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle278">&#x202a;不過這本筆記本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11028350000t" end="11064300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle279">&#x202a;讓人有一種&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;無論如何都想嘗試看看的魔力&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11086400000t" end="11125990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle280">&#x202a;我…我殺人了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;還殺了兩個人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11135120000t" end="11148090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle281">&#x202a;我居然會殺人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11168150000t" end="11192830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle282">&#x202a;人命是很珍貴的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11203520000t" end="11234120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle283">&#x202a;我有擅自製裁別人的權利嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11260910000t" end="11281160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle284">&#x202a;不,不是的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11289270000t" end="11309860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle285">&#x202a;我不是一直在想這些嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11310960000t" end="11331210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle286">&#x202a;這個世界爛透了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11332320000t" end="11353250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle287">&#x202a;爛人還是死了比較好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11363680000t" end="11377670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle288">&#x202a;一定要…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11378700000t" end="11406000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle289">&#x202a;一定要有人來做這件事才可以&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11407060000t" end="11434360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle290">&#x202a;就算他會犧牲我的精神和性命&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11442430000t" end="11465750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle291">&#x202a;不能再讓世界沉淪下去了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11479130000t" end="11514400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle292">&#x202a;如果這本筆記本&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;被別人撿走了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11515500000t" end="11551110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle293">&#x202a;誰有這種能耐&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;消滅世界上不需要的人?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11552200000t" end="11563460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle294">&#x202a;不可能有這種人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11572890000t" end="11601560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle295">&#x202a;可是如果是我,我就辦得到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11618940000t" end="11642940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle296">&#x202a;不,只有我能辦得到!&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11656640000t" end="11676550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle297">&#x202a;用死亡筆記本來執行吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11690010000t" end="11704680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle298">&#x202a;改變這個世界!&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12082730000t" end="12105370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle299">&#x202a;首先要為地球來個大掃除&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12106420000t" end="12131670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle300">&#x202a;不斷寫上兇惡罪犯的名字&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12132780000t" end="12162470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle301">&#x202a;這樣以後&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就沒有人敢做壞事了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12175830000t" end="12224180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle302">&#x202a;犯罪的壞人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我就讓他死於心臟痲痺&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12225210000t" end="12260130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle303">&#x202a;沒道德觀念的人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;和給別人帶來困擾的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12261240000t" end="12293210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle304">&#x202a;我就用病死或車禍死亡的死因&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;慢慢將他們消滅&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12294280000t" end="12304520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle305">&#x202a;這麼一來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12305620000t" end="12334290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle306">&#x202a;世界一定會往好的方向前進&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12344330000t" end="12353650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle307">&#x202a;然後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12354670000t" end="12404610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle308">&#x202a;和一群我也認同的善良人們&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;共同創造出新世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12413400000t" end="12446050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle309">&#x202a;到時候個性差勁的人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;只剩下你而已喔&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12459780000t" end="12489130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle310">&#x202a;路克,你在說什麼啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12490140000t" end="12530410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle311">&#x202a;我可是個認真的模範生喔&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;說是日本第一也不為過&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12555870000t" end="12567470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle312">&#x202a;而且我即將…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12593580000t" end="12609160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle313">&#x202a;成為新世界的神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12639620000t" end="12656230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle314">&#x202a;人類果然…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12672660000t" end="12684600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle315">&#x202a;很有意思&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12804120000t" end="12854400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle316">&#x202a;看見誰都無法看見的夢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12855500000t" end="12909200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle317">&#x202a;捨棄所有不需要的事物&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12910230000t" end="12942200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle318">&#x202a;無法割捨的感情&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12943260000t" end="12997640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle319">&#x202a;深藏在我的心裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12998650000t" end="13062360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle320">&#x202a;依然處在現實與理想的夾縫中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13063380000t" end="13114350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle321">&#x202a;即使犧牲的伽鎖拴住敢的腳&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13115430000t" end="13165710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle322">&#x202a;無法壓抑滿腔的衝動&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13166820000t" end="13234850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle323">&#x202a;因為我有一顆強烈追求的心&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13244560000t" end="13292230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle324">&#x202a;虛偽恐懼虛飾憂愁&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13293280000t" end="13347660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle325">&#x202a;面對各種負面情緒&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13348660000t" end="13402700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle326">&#x202a;我也不會弱到被擊垮&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13403720000t" end="13448090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle327">&#x202a;不知孤獨為何物Trickster&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13554540000t" end="13574220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle328">&#x202a;違逆我會有什麼下場?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13583570000t" end="13604840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle329">&#x202a;全世界都在屏息注目&#x202c;</p>
